---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

---

<Layout title="About">
  <p class="p-4 text-left">
    I am a CS student and self-driven developer with primary interest in web application development. I am expected to complete my Bachelor's degree from University of Debrecen in August 2024. This page is about my profile, feel free to take a look with a cup of tea &#9749;
  </p>
  <ul class="timeline relative list-none mt-4">
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/kyoto.jpg" alt="Kyoto">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>1998<br>Birth in Kyoto</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">My future dream was becoming a Ninja.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/surfing.jpg" alt="Surfing">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>2011~2014<br>Middle school</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">My father loves surfing and I got interested it too. I have enjoyed it even now!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/tennis.jpg" alt="Tennis">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>2014~2017<br>High school</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">I was a member of a tennis club, and it was a great experience collaborating with my
            doubles partner and teammates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/dear.jpg" alt="Dear">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>2017~2021<br>Rakuno University</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">I got into the University to learn about wildlife and nature since I love animals
            and wanted to preserve nature. When I was in 3rd year, I went to Malaysia as a exchange student, and I
            realize the importance of English. This experience inspired me to learn English, and start considering
            about study abroad.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/coding.jpg" alt="Coding">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>2021~2024<br>University of Debrecen</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">I decided to change my major because job oppotunities for IT industory is huge and
            IT career is quite interesting for me.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-img">
        <img class="round-img" src="images/future.jpg" alt="Future">
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-panel">
        <div class="timeline-heading">
          <h4>2024~<br>My future</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <p class="text-muted">My primary goal is to specialize in web and software development. I plan to achieve
            this by continuously advancing my skills through both on-the-job learning and self-study.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</Layout>

<style>
.timeline:before {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 80px;
  width: 4px;
  margin-left: -1.5px;
  content: "";
  background-color: #640075;
}

.timeline>li {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.timeline-panel {
  position: relative;
  float: right;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0 20px 0 180px;
  min-height: 200px;
}

.timeline-panel h4,
.timeline-panel p {
  text-align: left;
}

.timeline>li:after,
.timeline>li:before {
  display: table;
  content: "";
}

.timeline>li:after {
  clear: both;
}

.timeline-img {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 10;
  width: 160px;
  height: 160px;
  left: 0;
  margin-left: 0;
  border: 7px solid #640075;
  border-radius: 100%;
}

.round-img {
  border-radius: 50%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

/* iPhone X || 375 x 812 || Default */
@media only screen and (max-width: 812px) {
  .grid-container {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .timeline:before {
    left: 50%;
  }

  .timeline-panel {
    padding: 180px 2rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-panel h4,
  .timeline-panel p {
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .timeline-heading,
  .timeline-body {
    background-color: rgb(30 41 59);
    border: medium solid #640075;
  }

  .timeline-img {
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, 0);
  }
}
</style>
